data.description: Enjoy this newly renovated 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhouse with 1 attached garage located in a gated community. This townhouse is convenient and very close to shopping center, grocery stores, restaurants, schools, Parris Island and MCAS. There is a playground, clubhouse, and swimming pool to enjoy for the summer.
